text.__SUMMARY__: Shorea asahii is a species of plant in the Dipterocarpaceae family. It is endemic to Borneo.
text.Sources: Ashton, P. (1998). "Shorea asahii". The IUCN Red List of Threatened Species. IUCN. 1998: e.T33405A9780672. doi:10.2305/IUCN.UK.1998.RLTS.T33405A9780672.en. Retrieved 22 December 2017.
